Section 27-17-15

Applicability of Other Provisions to Chapter.

The following provisions of this title shall also apply as to burial insurance policies:

(1) Section 27-15-15;

(2) Section 27-15-24;

(3) Section 27-15-25;

(4) Section 27-15-29; and

(5) Section 27-16-16.

(Acts 1971, No. 407, p. 707, §406.)
